Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:03.35,0:00:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who wrote this love letter?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  That's right.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you... give me an answer?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:13.14,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it'll be a good one.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:15.50,0:00:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I don't really know you very well.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.27,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:21.59,0:00:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... are you really okay with someone like me?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want anyone else.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:28.45,0:00:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the one I like...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I no good?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.64,0:00:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm overjoyed to be able to date a cute girl like you!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:39.15,0:00:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... cute?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:44.00,0:00:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're fine with me...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.21,0:00:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:53.92,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.19,0:00:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy I was able to tell you my feelings.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:59.31,0:01:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kamizaki Risa from class 2-B...
Dialogue: 3,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be your girlfriend starting today, Tachibana Junichi!
Dialogue: 3,0:01:07.73,0:01:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything if it'll make you happy.
