Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to try your Oden, Hibiki-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.  Looks like we ran out of time.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
