Dialogue: 3,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come here again during lunch tomorrow?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue from where we left off then.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow at lunch, I'm gonna continue from where I left off with Risa-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1600 AD, in the battle of Sekigahara...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:30.89,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably introduce Risa-chan to Umehara and Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been worried about me since that Christmas incident two years ago...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:42.75,0:03:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this year's Christmas will be a happy one.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.80,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've have a really cute girlfriend now!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally lunchtime!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to meet up with Risa-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You're already here?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I couldn't wait to see you, Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:07.28,0:04:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait to see you too,\Nso I came here as fast as I could...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you beat me to it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that you came.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I'd come!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.48,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I'm also really happy I could see you, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lovers, aren't we?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:28.29,0:04:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when did you first start to... um... like me?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since a long time ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.08,0:04:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:36.76,0:04:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching you, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:42.24,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... can I ask you something too?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:47.11,0:04:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are my boobs kinda small?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer big ones, don't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I don't have much of a chest...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.46,0:05:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like bigger is better.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.41,0:05:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think there are nice things about small ones too...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to pretend.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.74,0:05:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you like bigger ones.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you once before...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were reading that kind of book at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.60,IdolTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\an9\fs40\c&HE0B5F5&\bord4\3c&H58437B&}Big boobs idol
Dialogue: 3,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... that was um...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Umehara likes!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That doesn't mean I like the same thing!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm sure guys like them big.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine are small now, but I'm working hard.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:31.98,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still growing too.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... wait a little longer, okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's not like I like big ones that mu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what do you mean by working hard?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm doing all kinds of things...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan, I'd like to introduce you to my friends...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:53.15,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing I can't do.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:03.10,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let anyone know that we're dating.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.18,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to make sure nobody sees us when we meet.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.15,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only meet in this unused preparation room in school.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:24.50,0:06:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that we're dating, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:31.28,0:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet, we'll meet somewhere secluded.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.36,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to keep that promise, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:05.55,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody comes here at night, so I don't think anyone will see us together here.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this place is okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:13.81,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a date... right?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a date.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.67,0:07:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you fine with this place, Tachibana-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:26.21,0:07:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a place you like very much.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about what happened two years ago?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stood up here on Christmas Eve two years ago.{lit: rejected}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:41.31,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's true that my memories of this place aren't exactly great.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:49.17,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember this place as the place where I had my first date with you, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.88,ChalkboardTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\fs55)\alpha&H80&\blur0.9\fax-0.3\fay-0.28\move(161,531,211,534,0,1740)}2 days until the\NFounder's Festival!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:05.00,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Founder's Festival the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I still don't have a nice girlfriend.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by some freak chance I don't\Nfind one before the day arrives...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind walking around the place with you, boss.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I were to suddenly find an awesome girlfriend...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you'll have to walk around on your own.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big words, buddy!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:33.99,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about putting meat buns in the Oden?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go to the Founder's Festival with you tomorrow...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, it's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:47.28,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to tour the festival with you too, Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.29,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since my heart was broken two years ago, Umehara's always been looking out for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:58.64,0:09:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a cute girlfriend now.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to let him know I'm okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me think about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:06.68,0:09:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know before the Founder's Festival tomorrow.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to go to the Founder's Festival with Risa-chan tomorrow?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm finally Tachibana-kun's girlfriend, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd want to go to the festival with him!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.85,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want all the girls to see he's my boyfriend so they'll know to keep their hands off!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:42.39,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let people know that I'm his girlfriend at this point.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:47.39,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done horrible things to every girl who got close to him...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purr, meow!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he getting along so well with Morishima-senpai?!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.45,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she already reject him?!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.08,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.15,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I loved it!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might grow close and even start dating at this rate!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:07.76,0:10:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be hurt like he was two years ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have some business with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:18.39,0:10:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'd like you to look at this.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a picture of Tachibana-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:25.44,0:10:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And could this girl with him in the picture be...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she seems to be his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:30.63,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So after seeing the two of you get along so well, I felt the need to let you know.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was surprised myself.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:41.80,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have nothing more to say now that I've seen this photo.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.45,0:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to stay away from him so I don't give him the wrong impression.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:54.33,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's for the best.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.47,0:11:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, why is she being so friendly with him at work?!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, do your damn job!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.73,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're supposed to just be friends!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just ignore this.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what I think it is?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it is.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you didn't seem to know about it, Tanamachi-san...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me know.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a baby.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should've just told me he already had somebody.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was working myself up...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like such a fool.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's for the best.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.11,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructor, I see her as a vending machine!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.91,0:11:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now he's getting close with that underclassman?!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.19,Alternate,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now try again!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Tachibana-kun is a wonderful person...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't good!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for her since she seems like a timid girl, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the best.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yes?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks really shocked.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:01.93,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll find someone else right away since she's so cute.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her boobs are huge though.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:09.22,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Tachibana-kun really prefers girls with bigger boobs...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.81,0:12:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm sorry, but could you wait outside until practice is over?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making Tachibana-kun wait until practice is over?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's already acting like she's his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun already has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not really my place to have told you this...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't really matter to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me know.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful not to give him the wrong impression.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  It didn't seem like much of a shock to her.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:50.07,0:12:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't feel quite as bad for doing this...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.53,0:12:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}was{\i0\fscx130} {\r}a shock to her...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.54,0:13:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's supposed to just be his childhood friend, but they've suddenly gotten really close!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let this continue.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:06.46,0:13:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt her since she's my classmate, but...{but I totally will XP}
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:12.08,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai-san, cheer up!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.46,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you come with me like this.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking advantage of Tachibana-kun's good nature and working him so hard...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.86,Alternate2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.  Let me know if you need anything else.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:20.36,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's been using him after he\Njoined the committee to do all kinds of work.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.32,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is she after Tachibana-kun himself?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I must do something!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san, so that's who you're really are...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:38.19,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a completely different person!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.52,0:13:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd have no problems deceiving Tachibana-kun for sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to protect him.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that incident two years ago had never happened...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:51.38,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've just confessed to him normally without having to get in everyone's way.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Tachibana-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makihara... san?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're attending Kibitou right now?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform looks good on you.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're attending Kibina?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's close to where I live.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:22.43,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Makihara-san able to speak to me so casually?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:27.18,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who stood me up for our Christmas date two years ago...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:34.15,0:14:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've always\Nwanted to ask you, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day... Christmas, two years ago...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you show up where we were supposed to meet?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  But...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited in this park the whole time!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:52.23,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you change the meeting place?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did that.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:57.50,0:15:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a girl in our class told me you\Nwanted to change the meeting spot.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting in front of the cinema for ages.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how that happened.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you know her?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:10.63,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't exactly stand out very much, but that one girl...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.60,FestivalTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax0.1\fay0.07\blur1.1\move(1170,158,1129,158,0,1986)\c&HD7D8F6&\3c&H343469&\frz359.591}Kibitou High School\NFounder's Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.60,FestivalTS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax0.1\fay0.07\blur1.1\frz359.591\move(1175,160,1134,160,0,1986)\alpha&HFF&\c&H8B8B99&\3c&H575763&}Kibitou High School\N{\alpha&H40&}Founder's Festival
Dialogue: 3,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:27.73,0:15:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think about going to the festival with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.30,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The festival doesn't matter as long as you're by my side, Tachibana-kun...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:36.86,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you don't want to be seen with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.62,0:15:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we don't make a good couple...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:49.89,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't have the right to date you.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hiding from me, Risa-chan?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd hate me if you knew everything.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want to tell you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Risa.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:08.15,0:16:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So seeing you suffer alone like this is hard on me too.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please tell me.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:14.69,0:16:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:18.27,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you were stood up on Christmas two years ago...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my fault.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she was waiting with all her classmate friends at the meeting place...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was going to dump you right there.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.46,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were going to make a joke out of your date invitation simply to have some fun.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like you remember...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:40.92,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was in the same class as you at the time, and they invited me as well.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've always truly loved you, Tachibana-kun,
Dialogue: 3,0:16:52.50,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to give up if she actually loved you.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:56.46,0:17:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I lied to Makihara-san that you had changed the location.{lit: That's why I told her that you told me to tell Makihara-san that you'd changed the location to a bogus place}
Dialogue: 3,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Risa-chan was who Makihara-san was talking about.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:07.45,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, you were terribly hurt that day.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:13.08,0:17:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I felt responsible that I wasn't able to protect you that day...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And decided never to confess my feelings to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:20.32,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But recently you seemed ready to move on from what happened two years ago.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actively got friendly with other girls.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I started to think...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:30.45,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Tachibana-kun gets hurt by another girl again?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:34.69,0:17:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I thought of becoming your\Ngirlfriend and protecting you forever!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.55,0:17:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered my courage and confessed to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:49.17,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, what's the problem with us going out?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.05,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makihara-san's attending a different school, and I barely see her.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:00.85,0:18:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, whenever it seemed like things were going well between you and a girl...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intervened.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:07.89,0:18:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them you already had a girlfriend and showed them a doctored photo.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I said.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.69,0:18:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't trust any girl other than myself to not hurt you.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:22.67,0:18:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I ended up hurting many other girls.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself it was to protect you...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:30.71,0:18:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, maybe I was just jealous of them.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want them to take you from me.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:37.35,0:18:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I did all that, I can't just tell them we're dating.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care for me so much?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like you remember...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was in the same elementary school as you too.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:53.53,0:18:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I transferred in, though that was during mid-year...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a rather plain girl after all.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:03.66,0:19:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was when I'd just transferred in, had no friends, and didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.84,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were really strict about leaving food on your tray in that school, remember?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.61,0:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't handle milk very well...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we weren't allowed to leave anything on our tray.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.48,0:19:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was a boy who'd drink it for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, you'd always come and drink my milk for me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what it looks like to others.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, it was something very special.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love with you ever since...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.79,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only had eyes for you.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:52.38,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I can't go with you to the Founder's Festival.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.34,0:20:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also really sorry you can't have a fun Christmas again this year because of me.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:03.09,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my dream came true in the short period where I was your girlfriend...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.52,0:20:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please find a girlfriend you can have fun with for next year's festival.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get in the way anymore.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:22.08,0:20:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll find someone wonderful right away.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.81,0:20:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa-chan, are you going to dump me too?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.94,0:20:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.98,0:20:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to leave me with\Nanother lonely Christmas memory?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:40.47,0:20:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't want to.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of being lonely at Christmas.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to always be by my side.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go apologize together.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together and apologize to the people you lied to.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:10.58,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's tell them that we're dating.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll forgive me?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:18.81,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand just how much you love me, Risa-chan.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:24.19,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You confessed out of the blue but didn't want anybody to know, so I wasn't really sure what you wanted.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:30.30,0:21:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I feel a lot better now that I know the truth.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:34.37,0:21:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wrap everything up so we can date with no regrets.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not together.
